  "content": "<p><strong>My Etsy Picks: Fall Faves</strong></p>\n<p>As you can tell by my previous posts, Fall is my absolute favorite! While I’m not quite ready to get back full time to blogging (unpacking rules my life right now), I thought I’d take a break and peruse all the fine wares on Etsy that are dedicated to the Autumn.</p>\n<p>You can check out the <em><a title=\"Etsy Treasury: Fall Faves by Katie Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyNDI5NjcyNw/fall-faves\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">original treasury right here</a>,</em> and you’ll find a list of the above shops below! How cute are these items! I want them ALL!! Pop in to these shops and fave an item or two- these talented Etsy artists certainly deserve it!</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Chics Who Craft on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/162597512/fall-burlap-banner-fall-sign?ref=listing-shop-header-0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Chics Who Craft</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"CCWD on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/106841771/primitive-candy-corn-shelf-sitter?ref=sr_gallery_27&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=2&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CCWD</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Rhonda's Treasures on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/112007191/pumpkin-necklace-genuine-howlite-fall?ref=sr_gallery_26&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=3&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rhonda’s Treasures</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Take Flyte Farm on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/161104583/fall-halloween-pumpkin-fun-painted?ref=sr_gallery_27&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Take Flyte Farm</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Merry Merry's Handmades on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/103350901/baby-boy-halloweenfall-one-piece?ref=sr_gallery_26&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=6&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Merry’s Merry Handmades</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Jalipeno on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/165622071/fall-festival-printable-poster-flyer?ref=sr_gallery_26&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=12&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Jalipeno</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Tikkido on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/114125267/felt-acorn-fall-thanksgiving-napkin-ring?ref=sr_gallery_36&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=14&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tikkido</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Knits by Vara on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/110313934/owl-fingerless-gloves-knit-fingerless?ref=sr_gallery_34&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=3&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Knits by Vara</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Crimson Hill on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/57777165/pumpkin-soap-fall-autumn-halloween-gift?ref=sr_gallery_15&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=2&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Crimson Hill</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Soda City Sewing on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/162832335/reversible-fall-boys-longall-with?ref=sr_gallery_6&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Soda City Sewing</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Silent Roses on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/85199758/autumn-fall-necklace-maple-leaf-leaves?ref=sr_gallery_11&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=11&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Silent Roses</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Wood 'n Stitches on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/110890350/primitive-autumn-happy-fall-yall-wood?ref=sr_gallery_12&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=14&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wood ‘n Stitches</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"D'Rae Designs on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/85199758/autumn-fall-necklace-maple-leaf-leaves?ref=sr_gallery_11&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=11&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">D’Rae Designs</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Little Life Designs on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/162085306/fall-word-art-give-thanks-fall-decor?ref=sr_gallery_4&ga_search_query=autumn+decor&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=1&ga_ref=related&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Little Life Designs</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Englert & Englert on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/107845084/fall-pumpkin-block-set?ref=sr_gallery_35&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_page=8&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Englert & Englert</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Picket Fence Confections\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/107723877/fall-leaves-pumpkin-and-acorn-sugar?ref=sr_gallery_18&ga_search_query=fall&ga_show_panel=true&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Picket Fence Confections</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Hope you liked my Fall fave picks! I’ll be sure to do a Halloweeeeeen themed one in a few weeks!</p>\n<p>Which Fall item was your favorite?</p>\n",
